      "text": [
        "1721 - وَ قَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «ضَمِنْتُ لِمَنِ اِقْتَصَدَ أَنْ لاَ يَفْتَقِرَ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1721 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"I guarantee for the one who practices moderation that they will not face poverty.\""
        ]
      }
    }
